<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$dark-cui" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/dark-cui" class="zg-link" title="Dark Cui">Dark Cui</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhang-mu-zhi-77" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhang-mu-zhi-77" class="zg-link" title="张牧之">张牧之</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$lee-gavin-20" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/lee-gavin-20" class="zg-link" title="Lee Gavin">Lee Gavin</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


